### Create priced draft order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: local-create-order

{
  "retailerId": "{{retailerId}}",
  "outletId": "{{outletId}}",
  "requestedDeliveryDate": "2030-12-31",
  "lines": [
    {
      "skuId": "{{skuId}}",
      "quantity": 3.000
    }
  ]
}

### List orders
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders
X-Correlation-Id: local-list-orders

### Get order
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/{{orderId}}
X-Correlation-Id: local-get-order

### Submit order and reserve stock
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/{{orderId}}/submit
Idempotency-Key: local-submit-order-1
X-Correlation-Id: local-submit-order

### Order timeline
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/{{orderId}}/timeline
X-Correlation-Id: local-order-timeline
